snippet.title: Marvel Heroes - Opening Cinematic - Marvel Origins
snippet.description:
Welcome to Marvel Heroes (www.marvelheroes.com), the free to play action MMO action RPG from Gazillion Entertainment! In this epic conclusion to the story begun in the Chronicles of Doom, we meet Uatu, the Watcher - observer of the Marvel Universe. But soon, battle-lines are drawn as Doctor Doom possesses the Cosmic Cube - and the Watcher can watch no longer!

Want more? The incredible story continues in Marvel Heroes - available to play today at www.marvelheroes.com!

Written by Brian Michael Bendis, and produced by Gazillion Entertainment.
